ll, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O God, I adjure You by the right of the Arsh and the one, who raised it, and by the right of revelation and by one, who sent; and by the right of the Prophet and one, who made him a prophet; and by the right of Kaaba and one, who made it. O one, who listens to every voice. O one, who gathers all that are lost. O one, who revives the souls after death, bless Muhammad and his Ahle Bayt.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Parwardigaar! Arsh aur uske buland karne waale ka waasta, wahee aur uske naazil karne waale ka waasta, nabi aur nabuwat dene waale ka waasta, Baiytullah aur uske taameer karne waale ka waasta. Ay har awaaz ke soonne waale, aur har goom-shudah ko daryaaft karne waale, ay marne ke baad jaano ko zindah karne waale, Muhammad (s.a.w.a) wa Aale Muhammad (a.s) par durood bhej.", "Urdu": "اے پروردگار! عرش اور اس کے بلند کرنے والے کا واسطہ، وحی اور اس کے نازل کرنے والے کا واسطہ نبی اور نبوت دینے والے کا واسطہ، بیت اللہ اور س کے تعمیر کرنے والے کا واسطہ۔ اے ہر آواز کے سننے والے، اور ہر گمشدہ کو دریافت کرنے والے، اے مرنے کے بعد جانوں کے زندہ کرنے والے، محمد و آل محمد پر درود بھیج۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA BE-HAQQIL A’RSHE WA MAN A’LAAHO, WA BE-HAQQIL WAHYE WA MAN AWHAAHO, WA BE-HAQQIN NABIYYE WA MAN NABBAAHO, WA BE-HAQQIL BAYTE WA MAN NABAAHO, YAA SAAME-A’ KULLE SAWTIN, YAA JAAME-A’ KULLE FAWTIN, YAA BAARE-AN NOFOOSE BA’DAL MAWTE, SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIN WA AHLE BAYTEHI.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ بِحَقِّ الْعَرْشِ وَمَنْ عَلَاہُ، وَبِحَقِّ الْوَحْيِ وَمَنْ اَوْحَاہُ، وَبِحَقِّ النَّبِيِّ وَمَنْ نَبَّاہُ، وَبِحَقِّ الْبَیْتِ وَمَنْ بَنَاہُ، یَا سَامِعَ كُلِّ صَوْتٍ، یَا جَامِعَ كُلِّ فَوْتٍ، یَا بَارِءَ النُّفُوْسِ بَعْدَ الْمَوْتِ، صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاَهْلِ بَیْتِهٖ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1011616, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "And grant from your side to me and the believer men and women of the east and the west of the world immediate tranquility and peace. I adjure by the right of ‘there is no god, except Allah and Muhammad is the messenger of Allah’. May Allah have mercy on Muhammad and his purified progeny and convey my salutation to them in excess.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aur Mashriq o Maghrib mein tamaam momin mardo’n aur aurto’n ko jaldi se Apni baargah se rehaayi farma. Is gawahi ke saath keh Allah ke siwa koi ma’bood nahi hai aur Muhammad (s.a.w.a) Tere bande aur rasool hai, un par aur unke taiyyab o taahir awlaad par durood o salaam ho.", "Urdu": "مجھے اور مشرق و مغرب میں تمام مومن مردوں اور عورتوں کو جلدی سے اپنی بارگاہ سے رہائی فرما۔ اس گواہی کے ساتھ کہ اللہ کے سوا کوئی معبود نہیں ہے اور محمد تیرے بندے اور رسول ہیں، ان پر اور ان کی طیب و طاہر اولاد پر درود و سلام ہو۔", "RArabic": "WA AATENAA WA JAMEE-A’L MOAMENEENA WAL MOAMENAATE FEE MASHAAREQIL ARZE WA MAGHAAREBEHAA FARAJAN MIN I’NDEKA A’AJELAN BE-SHAHAADATE AN LAA ELAAHA ILLAL LAAHO, WA ANNA MOHAMMADAN A’BDOKA WA RASOOLOKA SALLAL LAAHO A’LAYHE WA AALEHI, WA A’LAA ZURRIYYATEHIT TAYYEBEENAT TAAHEREENA, WA SALLAMA TASLEEMAN KASEERAN.", "ArabicText1": "وَآتِنَا وَجَمِیْعَ الْمُؤْمِنِیْنَ وَالْمُؤْمِنَاتِ، فِيْ مَشَارِقِ الْاَرْضِ وَمَغَارِبِهَا، فَرَجًا مِنْ عِنْدِكَ عَاجِلًا، بِشَهَادَةِ اَنْ لَا اِلٰهَ اِلَّا اللهُ، وَاَنَّ مُحَمَّدًا عَبْدُكَ وَرَسُوْلُكَ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَیْهِ وَاٰلِهٖ، وَعَلٰى ذُرِّیَّتِهِ الطَّیِّبِیْنَ الطَّاهِرِیْنَ، وَسَلَّمَ تَسْلِیْمًا كَثِیْرًا۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3":